description: These high grade GLS Audio Black Chrome Series "Generation 4" banana plugs are perfect for the audiophile do-it-yourselfer! They will accept wire gauge size of 10G, 12G, 14G, 16G, and 18G. The 24k gold plating will ensure a corrosion free connection. The plugs are made out of the highest grade of H59-1 brass. This BS20 is an 20 pack. You will receive 10 Red Banana Plugs and 10 Black Banana Plugs.
title: GLS Audio Black Chrome Series Generation 4 Gold Connector Banana Plugs Banana Clips - 20 Pack (10 Red & 10 Black)
